title: DARK SIDE REY: EVERYTHING WE KNOW | Star Wars: The Rise of Skywalker Theories, Palpatine, and More!
author: Think Story
comment: I don't cling to the theory that Rey's parents have to be special. However , Kylo has plenty of motivation to lie to her to get her on his side.
Honestly, how many good guys have you seen with a red lightsaber?
I say 2 realistic options. 1. It's just a force vision/flashback, etc. 2. She's possessed or taken over by Palpatatine against her will. She just has that vacant look in her eye.
I predict another fan meltdown coming.
description:
In this video we analyze everything we know so far about Dark Side Rey from the latest Star Wars: The Rise of Skywalker D23 trailer. Is it a vision or does she actually go to the side?
